SexyPermalinks
==============

Turns plain id-ending URLs into "sexy" links with more texty goodness.

Example
=======

page = Page.new(:title => 'This is an awesome page') # => page #1 created
link_to 'click here', page_path(page) # => '/pages/1-this-is-an-awesome-page'


